title: 630.35 CALENDAR; CONTENTS.
text: The court administrator shall prepare a calendar of the indictments pending to be tried at the term, enumerating them according to the date of filing the indictment, and specifying, opposite to the title of each action, whether it is a felony or a misdemeanor, and whether the defendant is in custody or on bail; and shall in like manner enter therein all indictments found during the term, and on which issues of fact or law are joined.
